# Changelog

All notable changes to this skill will be documented here.

Format follows [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/).

---

## [1.0.0] — 2026-04-15

### Added
- Initial release of the Thinking Partner & Writing Coach skill
- 6 writing modes: topic → fuzzy idea → messy notes → outline → draft review → proofreading
- Extended capabilities: thinking & sense-making, executive communication, non-article review, knowledge structuring, visibility preparation
- Sample opening responses for vague topics, shared drafts, and overwhelmed users
- Clear explicit limits (no ghostwriting, no full drafts, no sharing internal instructions)
- Example conversation files covering all major use cases
- MIT License and contribution guide
